08:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打完一場lol 個心都跳得好快<br />\n打多場就要休息 個腦好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備 Penta Kill 果下仲驚過連入五球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始就要最少打廿分鐘 廿分鐘都要keep住咁hyper唔易<br />\n再講 邊有咁多場廿分鐘 場場都三四十分鐘<br />\n又要操作又要溝通真心要技術<br />\n<br />\nBlueball就唔同 十分鐘一節 仲要成鳩日都換人<br />\n成場追住個波就得 毫無技術可言<br />\n加上場場都大比數對大比數 毫無刺激感"},{"pid":"40dd30803540f35df0d2f5943be5dc2fe8e3c33e","tid":158350,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打完一場lol 個心都跳得好快<br />\n打多場就要休息 個腦好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n準備 Penta Kill 果下仲驚過連入五球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始就要最少打廿分鐘 廿分鐘都要keep住咁hyper唔易<br />\n再講 邊有咁多場廿分鐘 場場都三四十分鐘<br />\n又要操作又要溝通真心要技術<br />\n<br />\nBlueball就唔同 十分鐘一節 仲要成鳩日都換人<br />\n成場追住個波就得 毫無技術可言<br />\n加上場場都大比數對大比數 毫無刺激感</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n講得無錯"},{"pid":"9b4683ce72a6775a42063d9aec309ecfa9f9718b","tid":158350,"uid":28041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"0負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793ef09a69980a47983a3a24df834207515347af","tid":158350,"uid":38543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"玩兩場lol已經扯晒蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7434f3f749ee0698218630ed4bafea1f63b7a07c","tid":158350,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩兩場lol已經扯晒蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo